+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

If used with non-threaded Tcl or an executable that is
not linked with libpthread then it will be necessary to
set "LD_PRELOAD=/usr/lib/libpthread.so" in the environment.
